# Repo shape

- apps/
  - api/ (NestJS)
  - ui/ (Next.js)
  - workflows/ (Temporal)
- packages/ are reusable libraries. apps/* are deployables.

## Conventions

- Run scripts from repo root using pnpm filtering.
- packages/ must never import from apps/.
- apps/ may depend on packages/ but not on sibling apps/.

## Quality bar

- If behavior changes, update or add tests.
- No secrets in logs. No tokens or credentials in code.
- Keep diffs small and PR-sized.
